{"word":"Eshtemoa","slug":"eshtemoa","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Eshtemoa</b> <a href=\"#/H851\">H851</a> <br/> 1. Called Eshtemoh<br/> - A town of Canaan assigned to Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=50'>Jos 15:50</a> <br/> - Allotted to the Aaronites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=14'>Jos 21:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=57'>1Ch 6:57</a> <br/> - David shared spoil with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=30&verse=28'>1Sa 30:28</a> <br/> 2. A descendant of Ezra<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=17'>1Ch 4:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=19'>1Ch 4:19</a>"}]}